      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "2463cf0db08cd071",
      "text": "The issue's \"place\" in the network will thus be established. This \"place\" will, in these straightforward instances, be congruent with an existing node which will be the \"pattern\" of the issue - in other words, nothing about the new issue will be significantly disruptive of the network, as its \"place\" will turn out to be a known pattern."
